  "description": "<i>Smart Mouse</i> is a single-screen maze action game with puzzle elements. The player controls a mouse who must navigate a maze filled with enemies. The mouse can push the blocks which make up the maze walls; a moving block will keep moving until it hits another block, and crush every enemy in its path. After squashing the last enemy in a level, the player moves on to the next. There are a total of 100 levels, and the player is able to save their progress using passwords.",
